Package org.fao.oekc.autotagger.main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DownloadFiles
    Starting from a text file containing the list of files to be downloaded (NewLine separator), downloads these files in a specific directory and converts the file to TXT (supported files: PDF, TXT, HTML).
    MauiAutoTaggerKey
    Given the path with the source text files, generates the .key files with agrovoc en tagging
    ProduceMappingTable
    Create text file of couples, with the symbol "=" as a separator: the key is the URL of the document, the value is a list of keywords with comma-space ", " separated values.
